name: The Best Engine Sounds of 2014 ᴴᴰ
description:
As promised, here is my annual compilation of the best airplane engine sounds in the videos uploaded to my channel over the past year. The clips are arranged chronologically by the date they were shot, and I'm sure you'll recognize most of them. So, without further ado, enjoy my first upload of 2015!

Thanks for watching! Please comment, rate, and subscribe!
